From 239a84e25502246ad90afc71c2f949c694b0e5e7 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Elias Ellison <elias.ellison@gmail.com>
Date: Wed, 15 Jul 2026 01:37:08 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] [inductor] Scalar/online-softmax reduction codegen
 (prerequisite for online-softmax fast-combine PR)

Minimal scaffolding carved from the June 2026 mega-commit 97385fb3273:
- config.triton.scalar_reduction_accumulators flag
- the reduction() codegen rewrite in codegen/triton.py adding the scalar
  online-softmax path (_block_max / running-max loop) and the interleaved
  scalar accumulator + online_softmax_cross_entropy codegen.

This is the codepath the fast-combine PR (a26fc2c8bf4) patches; it is carried
whole as an indivisible method rewrite.

written with claude code
